		"name": "HelpCenter",
		"description": "# üìò HelpCenter API Documentation\n\nBase URL: `http://your-domain.com/api`\n\nAuthentication: **Token-based** using `auth:sanctum`\n\n---\n\n## üßë‚Äçüíª Authentication\n\n### üîê Register\n\n**POST** `/auth/register`\n\n#### Body\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"phone_number\": \"+1234567890\",\n  \"password\": \"password\",\n  \"password_confirmation\": \"password\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n#### Response\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"message\": \"Registered successfully\",\n  \"token\": \"your_auth_token\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n### üîê Login\n\n**POST** `/auth/login`\n\n#### Body\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n#### Response\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"message\": \"Login successful\",\n  \"token\": \"your_auth_token\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n### üö™ Logout\n\n**POST** `/auth/logout`\n\nüîí Auth required\n\n#### Response\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"message\": \"Logged out successfully\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n### üë§ Profile\n\n**GET** `/auth/profile`\n\nüîí Auth required\n\n#### Response\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"phone_number\": \"+1234567890\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## üìö Categories\n\n### üìÑ All Categories\n\n**GET** `/categories`\n\n#### Response\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"name\": \"Technical Support\"\n  }\n]\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## ‚ùì FAQs\n\n### üìÑ All FAQs\n\n**GET** `/faqs`\n\n#### Response\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit[\n  {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"question\": \"How to reset password?\",\n    \"answer\": \"Go to settings > reset password\",\n    \"category\": {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"name\": \"Account\"\n    }\n  }\n]\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## üé´ Tickets\n\n### üÜï Create Ticket\n\n**POST** `/tickets`\n\nüîí Auth required\n\n#### Body\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"title\": \"Problem with login\",\n  \"description\": \"I cannot log into my account\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n#### Response\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"message\": \"Ticket created successfully\",\n  \"ticket\": {\n    \"id\": 1,\n    \"title\": \"Problem with login\",\n    \"status\": \"open\"\n  }\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n### üìÑ View All Tickets\n\n**GET** `/tickets`\n\nüîí Auth required\n\n---\n\n### üìÑ View Single Ticket\n\n**GET** `/tickets/{id}`\n\nüîí Auth required\n\n---\n\n### ‚úèÔ∏è Update Ticket\n\n**PUT** `/tickets/{id}`\n\nüîí Auth required\n\n#### Body\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"title\": \"New title\",\n  \"description\": \"Updated description\",\n  \"status\": \"closed\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## üí¨ Replies\n\n### üÜï Create Reply\n\n**POST** `/replies`\n\nüîí Auth required\n\n#### Body\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit{\n  \"ticket_id\": 1,\n  \"message\": \"This is my reply to the ticket\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n### üìÑ View All Replies for Ticket\n\n**GET** `/replies/{ticket_id}`\n\nüîí Auth required\n\n---\n\n## ‚úÖ Status Enum Values (for `status` field in Tickets)\n\n```\njsonCopyEdit[\n  \"open\",\n  \"pending\",\n  \"closed\"\n]\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## üîë Headers (for authenticated requests)\n\n```\nmakefileCopyEditAuthorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN\nAccept: application/json\n\n ```\n\n> &lt;p &gt;Created by Muhammed Salama ‚úåÔ∏è&lt;/p&gt;",
